          "text": "CREATE   PROCEDURE [CrisNationalGridWest].[usp_UpdateAccountTripNumberUsingUploadedMeterReadWorkDay]\nAS\r\n--**************************************************************************************\r\n--* Name:         \r\n--*\r\n--* Description:  Not Used\r\n---*               \r\n--* Exec:       \t\t[CrisNationalGridWest].[usp_UpdateAccountTripNumberUsingUploadedMeterReadWorkDay]\r\n--*\r\n--* Parameter(s):     \r\n--*\r\n--*\tSet ANSI_null on\r\n--*\tgo\r\n\r\n--* Database:     OEC\r\n--*\r\n--* Return:\t    0 Success\r\n--*                   9 Failure\r\n--*\r\n--* AUTHOR:       Peter Heller (PAH)\r\n--* Created On:   12/15/2011\r\n--**************************************************************************************\r\n--* Date         Tech Description of Change\r\n--* ---------- ----  -------------------------------------------------------------\r\n--* 12/15/2011 PAH  First Version \r\n--**************************************************************************************\r\n\r\n--**************************************************************************************\r\n--Declare Variables\r\n--**************************************************************************************\r\n--\r\n--**************************************************************************************\r\n--Set defaults\r\n--**************************************************************************************\r\n\r\n--**************************************************************************************\r\n--Main Process\r\n--**************************************************************************************\r\nBEGIN\r\n--\r\nupdate  Billing.Account\r\nset     TripNumber = CrisNationalGridWest.UploadAccountBillingDetail.MeterReadWorkDay ,\r\n        Notes = CrisNationalGridWest.UploadAccountBillingDetail.BillingPeriod\r\n        + ' - Tripnumber Changed from '\r\n        + cast(Billing.Account.TripNumber as varchar(3)) + ' to '\r\n        + cast(CrisNationalGridWest.UploadAccountBillingDetail.MeterReadWorkDay as varchar(3)) ,\r\n        FireAuditTrigger = 'Y' ,\r\n        LastUpdate = getdate() ,\r\n        AuthenticatedUserID = 1\r\nFROM CrisNationalGridWest.UploadAccountBillingDetail\r\n        inner join Billing.Account on CrisNationalGridWest.UploadAccountBillingDetail.AccountNumber = Billing.Account.OriginalAccountNumber\r\n                                      and CrisNationalGridWest.UploadAccountBillingDetail.MeterReadWorkDay <> Billing.Account.TripNumber\r\n                                      and CrisNationalGridWest.UploadAccountBillingDetail.ActivityDateTime is not null\r\n\r\nEND"
